org.apache.hadoop.hbase.coprocessor

Interface WALObserver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Coprocessor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseWALObserver

    @InterfaceAudience.LimitedPrivate(value="Coprocesssor")
 @InterfaceStability.Evolving
public interface WALObserver
extends Coprocessor
    It's provided to have a way for coprocessors to observe, rewrite, or skip WALEdits as they are being written to the WAL. Note that implementers of WALObserver will not see WALEdits that report themselves as empty via WALEdit.isEmpty(). RegionObserver provides hooks for adding logic for WALEdits in the region context during reconstruction, Defines coprocessor hooks for interacting with operations on the WAL.
